snippet.title: Best VGM 1405 - Yoshi's Island DS - Midboss Madness!
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 220 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kmkzuPrQHQM

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Nintendo DS
Yoshi's Island DS
Midboss Madness!
Yutaka Minobe
